{"tid":791327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央媒評論指山東水災需問責　文章數小時後被刪","createTime":"2018-08-23T16:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T11:27:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed742a29ad7e2c1badc12509ea32c818404bb696","tid":791327,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"【央媒評論指山東水災需問責　文章數小時後被刪】<br />\n【光明網：地方政府具懈怠心態，表現驚慌失措】<br />\n【學者：北方長期缺水，政府不敢貿然放水】<br />\n<br />\n上星期颱風溫比亞在上海登陸後，河南、河北、山東、安徽、江蘇等地，都下暴雨或特大暴雨。<br />\n<br />\n由上星期五到本星期一，山東省的折合降水量逾210億立方米，即逾17000個大明湖，創下1951年以來的最高紀錄，山東壽光市更加出現嚴重水災。這場大水災的成因，究竟是颱風降雨的天災，還是上游水庫洩洪造成的人禍呢？<br />\n<br />\n光明網星期四發表評論文章，指相比起南方的省份，山東遭遇的颱風較少，所以政府有忽視和懈怠心態。一旦降雨量超過預期，政府就會表現得驚慌失措，應對失據。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，直至星期二傍晚六點，水庫水量其實已接近庫底，但壽光市居然繼續洩洪，加重了下游村莊的災情，質問是誰做的決策。評論員認為要對失職官員問責，以及協助民眾追討賠償。不過，這篇文章好快就被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n北京工業大學建築工程學院退休教授周玉文認為，由於中國北方長期缺水，所以地方政府不敢貿然在事前放水，擔心庫存會白白流走。他舉例指，北京曾於颱風預報發出時，就把水庫的容量騰出來，結果颱風沒到，庫存弄了很多年沒還回來。<br />\n<br />\n周玉文估計，山東政府到溫比亞正式來襲，才發現水庫存量太多。由於水壩崩潰的損害更加嚴重，最後唯有緊急洩洪。<br />\n<br />\n#溫比亞<br />\n#水災<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"510f1123b3175b2432715ea0616b9e01fe5e9db4","tid":791327,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff811893c5c3226f509e0c1ad3f33632b846de7","tid":791327,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T22:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9764f56afbcc33f980fe412f45f4c85862a1d82c","tid":791327,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T22:55:55.000Z","msg":"實屬正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dd09509cae760d600b4e860e7cf31cef83774b","tid":791327,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:19:15.000Z","msg":"有免費水飲 仲唔多謝政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b1bc2b6a82ed068338fa9a8eb00dd1041f03d5","tid":791327,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378fb30fcbc84a652eb103aa145796b723b6c9f3","tid":791327,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:22:37.000Z","msg":"CCTVB唔敢報系列"},{"pid":"16bbfa062a14da53708512d4c3fdfe5a21d1af93","tid":791327,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058b2593a7c3de86e8c1b954ae349a9b40f301cc","tid":791327,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:02:45.000Z","msg":"民眾喜迎水位上漲"},{"pid":"b005d96d50d8a20a61cbfc228bcb1f6745144722","tid":791327,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"訓左無睇 TVB新聞講左未?"},{"pid":"9a85193a4c6aa1fd54fcedddf660bdbae8ef9bf6","tid":791327,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:22:57.000Z","msg":"北水黎，好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aaa71d63d4f03efe15a88f905078b8e22a43d3","tid":791327,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:23:47.000Z","msg":"水為財"},{"pid":"c329885ab57d7c4fdbea48b82424f06b534dcd8f","tid":791327,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14de812bab29ef7f33b0c05fed68053461ec4f8a","tid":791327,"uid":1411